<li>In UPEC and S. Typhimurium [ 9e12 ] , QseB is shown to be a negative regulator of bacterial motility , and a qseB mutant does not affect ﬂagellar gene-expression .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=28062286" target="_blank">28062286</a>]<br></li>
